p: Chemical analysis performed by GC-MS analysis of L. angustifolia EOs was represented in Scheme 3, which is characterized by the presence of many biologically important compounds listed in Table 5 such as hexanal, Eucalyptol, Lavandulyl acetate, Eugenol, Bicyclo[10.1.0]tridec-1-ene, Linoleic acid, and cis-11-Eicosenoic acid compounds that referenced with insecticide properties constituents.
